<h2>REAL ESTATE</h2>
<h3>Uncover The Hamptons Homes For Sale</h3>
<p>Real estate in The Hamptons awaits near Calgary&rsquo;s northernmost point. Bound by Stoney Trail to the west, Shaganappi Trail and Sarcee Trail to the west, and Country Hills Boulevard at the south, The Hamptons offers a peaceful suburban lifestyle complete with awe-inspiring views of the Rockies.</p>
<p>Homes for sale in The Hamptons are quite varied - from quaint condos and townhomes to stately luxury homes. New residential properties continue to flourish in The Hamptons, each with its own exquisite view of the golf course. Lots are typically between 44&rsquo;-48&rsquo;, backing onto beautiful green space. Active locals will love the easy access to over 30 acres of park land, and bike pathways that easily connect to the popular Nose Hill Park.</p>
<p>While luxury homes are plentiful in The Hamptons, this neighbourhood offers a range in prices to appeal to the needs of every resident. Condos and townhomes can be found for sale in the low $200,000s, while the average cost of a single-family detached property will be somewhere in line with $750,000. Some of the neighbourhood&rsquo;s most expensive properties approach the $1.5 million mark.</p>
</div>
